# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## 2.0.0 - 2021-02-08

### Added

- Add test page for production.
- Add test page to npm ignore list.
- Add isUndefined utility.

### Changed

- Rewrite main API, we use a function like jQuery to create alert instance so that we could create and manage a number of alert rather than change DOM of a single alert over and over again.
- Fixed error config in package.json and rollup.config.js.

### Removed 

- Remove useless editorconfig.
- Remove $$ utility.

## 1.0.1 - 2021-02-06

### Changed 

- Fix build error

## 1.0.0 - 2021-01-12

### Added

- Add rollup to build different targets.
- Add babel, eslint and prettier.
- Support `iife`, `umd`, `es` import so that you could use `<script>` or `import/require` to get the lib.

### Changed

- Change dir structure and npm scripts.


